          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 1,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "say": "Sakura Dorms - Souryuu's Room",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "story-1",
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "Why'd you come here by yourself, Z23? Aren't you usually always with your friends?",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "Ahaha... I wouldn't say \"always.\" Even I need some time for myself now and then.",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "paintingFadeOut": {
        "time": 0.5,
        "side": 1
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "And even though we're good friends, we sometimes get on each others' nerves.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "You have a point. I imagine it can be hard to deal with Ayanami and Laffey since they like to do things at their own pace.",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "Ah, um, it's not that bad. Compared to us, I'd say that the Sakura carriers have more than their fair share of... strong personalities.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "You don't have to pull your punches. *sigh*... We definitely do have a handful of oddballs...",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "Ahaha... I feel like we have a lot of common ground. Don't you ever get tired of dealing with the others?",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "I wouldn't say I get tired, but... Kaga's obsessed with combat, and let's not talk about Akagi...",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "Shoukaku won't stop poking and prodding at Akagi, and Zuikaku is a bit like my sister. Way too much energy.",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "*sigh*... Sometimes, I wonder if my reputation as a workaholic resulted from having to clean up after them...",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "Ahaha...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.2,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "You know what they say, \"you don't get to choose your own family.\" But, looking back, I don't think I'd want it any other way.",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "I totally get it, \"we're friends after all!\" \"Who the hell are you calling your friend?!\" That kind of dynamic!",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "I think it's a bit different for us. I wouldn't even say that we're \"friends.\"",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "But, there is a deeper bond connecting all of us.",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "A relationship that can't be described by words... That sounds a bit enviable when you put it that way.",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "I'm also a bit jealous of you and your friends. Hehe.",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "But more importantly... Commander, didn't anyone ever teach you that it's rude to eavesdrop?",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "Ah... Good morning, Commander!",
      "actor": 401230,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "say": "Good grief... But since you're already here, we might as well chat for a bit.",
      "actor": 307030,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Time flew as the three of us chatted the day away.",
      "blackBg": true,
      "bgName": "bg_story_room"
    }
  ],
